graph LR
    subgraph FE["前端系统 (Next.js on Vercel)"]
        Pages[静态页面<br/>SSG 构建产物]
        API[API Routes<br/>/api/contact]
        I18n[i18n 中间件<br/>next-intl]
        Components[React 组件<br/>12 个 Section]
    end

    subgraph ThirdParty["第三方系统"]
        ResendSvc[Resend<br/>邮件服务]
        CalendlySvc[Calendly<br/>预约服务]
    end

    subgraph Owner["站点所有者"]
        Inbox[邮件收件箱]
        Calendar[预约日历]
    end

    User((访客)) -->|HTTP/HTTPS| I18n
    I18n -->|语言路由| Pages
    Pages --> Components
    User -->|提交表单| API
    API -->|调用 SDK| ResendSvc
    ResendSvc -->|发送通知| Inbox
    User -->|嵌入交互| CalendlySvc
    CalendlySvc -->|预约确认| Calendar

    style FE fill:#EEF2FF,stroke:#1E3A8A,stroke-width:2px
    style ThirdParty fill:#F0F9FF,stroke:#3B82F6,stroke-width:2px
    style Owner fill:#F0FDF4,stroke:#22C55E,stroke-width:2px
